Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.90,0:00:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.83,0:00:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.54,0:00:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.42,0:00:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.16,0:00:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.03,0:00:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.67,0:00:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.07,0:00:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.18,0:01:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.35,0:01:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.78,0:01:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.19,0:01:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.93,0:01:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.33,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.80,0:01:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.35,0:01:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬鈴薯燉肉定食啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.12,0:01:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吃東西還是一樣\N像個鄉巴佬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.72,0:01:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你管!\N這個最容易填飽肚子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.63,0:01:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,筷子斷掉會倒大楣喔\N這是我奶奶說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.87,0:01:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不信呢,根本是無稽之談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.27,0:01:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你還是小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我奶奶是不會說謊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.35,0:02:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本那傢伙\N盡是說些有的沒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.29,0:02:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有受傷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.59,0:02:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你啊,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.86,0:02:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心手鬆掉了\N抱歉,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.90,0:02:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼抱歉抱歉啊,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.53,0:02:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,一百圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.27,0:02:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撿到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.51,0:02:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,筷子斷掉會倒大楣喔\N這是我奶奶說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.18,0:02:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.70,0:02:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#16 探病的衝擊!\N就算病倒也喜歡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.27,0:02:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.91,0:02:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要緊吧?音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.59,0:03:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.89,0:03:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.49,0:03:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會痛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會,有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.53,0:03:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扭傷了,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.46,0:03:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我發的球太猛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.80,0:03:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事\N是我自己球技不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.17,0:03:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.87,0:03:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別這麼說\N真的沒什麼大不了的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送妳去醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.65,0:03:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你把我放下來\N這樣太誇張了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.22,0:03:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也太露骨了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.82,0:03:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛在大家面前\N把她抱起來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.69,0:03:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳不要想歪了\N這也是教練的職責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.43,0:03:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,如果我受傷了\N你也會像這樣抱我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.70,0:03:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,不用勉強抬答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.48,0:04:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.12,0:04:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大大小小的事情都麻煩你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.45,0:04:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有困難的時候要互相幫忙嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.96,0:04:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳要快點好起來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.26,0:04:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.76,0:04:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,妳衣服換好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.16,0:04:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼還在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我抱妳到棉被裡去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,我自己來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦,不可以逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他要繞一圈呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去問這位大哥哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.91,0:04:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔,我都沒有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.12,0:04:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要順勢\N把她壓倒在棉被裡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真愛說笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓下去做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.26,0:04:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去問這位大哥哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太真是愛說笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,聽說妳受傷啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.34,0:05:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,一點小傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼受傷的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.77,0:05:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她跟我打球\N才變成這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.48,0:05:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過幸好有你在\N幫了一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說這個了\N今晚要不要住下來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.39,0:05:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要這樣\N現在我在跟音無小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐\N我會照顧妳到痊癒為止…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.69,0:05:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要不要住下來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.09,0:05:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,我會負責…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.13,0:05:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛,跟人家玩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.46,0:05:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會負責照顧妳…\N喂,妳不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.83,0:05:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照顧我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.00,0:05:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.64,0:05:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們別鬧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管他們,快點躺下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.21,0:05:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.01,0:05:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,病人就要好好休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.71,0:05:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.68,0:05:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點吵,不要在意\N稍微睡一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,喝酒吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.23,0:06:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是三鷹的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.03,0:06:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙這麼晚還在這裡幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.37,0:06:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無精打采的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.01,0:06:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是吃壞肚子了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.95,0:06:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情大條了,事情大條了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.18,0:06:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員也來喝一杯吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.92,0:06:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,我不能喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.02,0:06:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.06,0:06:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.43,0:06:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?妳生病了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的,其實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.87,0:06:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.93,0:06:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.24,0:06:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員的腳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.61,0:06:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.88,0:07:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我中午吃飯的時候\N把筷子折斷了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.09,0:07:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個腳傷是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.63,0:07:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我發球發得太猛\N害音無小姐扭傷了腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,是我自己不小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是,這都是我害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對,這明明就是我害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.84,0:07:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰害的有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.81,0:07:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了走了\N“鼓勵管理員宴會”結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經這麼晚了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了,響子\N請保重喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.86,0:07:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.73,0:07:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.59,0:07:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.76,0:07:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還在幹什麼\N宴會已經結束了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.80,0:07:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下\N我還有話要跟管理員說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有話跟我們說就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.81,0:07:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是,管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.82,0:08:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.32,0:08:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員會受傷,都是我害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要胡扯到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.39,0:08:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦\N都是我害管理員受傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,我要去照顧管理員才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.87,0:08:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想找藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.97,0:08:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會讓你趁機\N單獨進入管理員的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.57,0:08:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了,你在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.51,0:08:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你抱著枕頭要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去照顧她一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,喝酒喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等,我要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.65,0:08:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,來,喝酒喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.53,0:08:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.88,0:09:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪位?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳起來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.45,0:09:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起來了,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.46,0:09:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安,你今天起得真早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,是有點早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉色不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上沒睡好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我擔心妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.70,0:09:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麼我能做的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.04,0:09:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,妳是因為我才受傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.81,0:09:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我害的\N所以請讓我照顧妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.76,0:09:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你要去上課,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要請假,不去上課了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦,要認真上課才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.70,0:09:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很認真啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.43,0:10:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼\N居然跑到女生睡覺的房間來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.54,0:10:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代他是因為擔心我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.07,0:10:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,反正你也沒有膽子\N溜到棉被裡面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.28,0:10:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這話什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是一些現成的飯菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.61,0:10:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.85,0:10:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確都是現成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.78,0:10:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃這種東西\N管理員的傷怎麼會好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走,快點去上學吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.49,0:10:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好地照顧管理員的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.06,0:10:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你留在這裡\N她的傷又不會比較快好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.68,0:10:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.88,0:10:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯去吧,吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.98,0:10:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙慌慌張張地在忙什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.69,0:10:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,一刻館嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.06,0:10:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,你是四谷嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.99,0:11:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問管理員的情況怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.50,0:11:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她現在很好,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.73,0:11:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.17,0:11:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她今天中午有吃飯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.20,0:11:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊,吃很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她吃了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.61,0:11:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃了一個柴魚飯糰\N和一個梅子飯糰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有三片醃蘿蔔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.78,0:11:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?吃得這麼寒酸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.42,0:11:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.42,0:11:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早飯吃現成的飯菜\N中午吃飯糰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.26,0:11:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得想想辦法才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.76,0:11:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.06,0:12:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶油燉牛肉\N味道清爽是最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.33,0:12:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以材料不能用油煎\N要用葡萄酒慢慢燉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.93,0:12:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且要用小火慢慢燉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.80,0:12:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做的好道地喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做菜是一種藝術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要豐富的感性\N和優秀的創造力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.45,0:12:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不知道\N想不到你還會做菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.12,0:12:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來這下妳又多了解我一點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.89,0:12:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.73,0:12:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.00,0:12:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,請吃吃看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.27,0:12:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請吃,請吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.71,0:12:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.74,0:12:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很會做菜耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.32,0:13:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡做菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.82,0:13:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會不會不太像男人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.49,0:13:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,沒有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.29,0:13:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我真的很過意不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.79,0:13:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠這樣照顧妳\N我覺得是我的榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.10,0:13:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真噁心,居然滿口甜言蜜語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.74,0:13:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他父母是笨蛋嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.31,0:13:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係,長得帥就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.68,0:13:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看我也去受個傷好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.01,0:13:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去啊,妳會餓死的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.62,0:13:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,189圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.89,0:13:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,51圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,238圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.33,0:13:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,36圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.03,0:13:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一共623圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.30,0:13:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!這麼多?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.07,0:13:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一共623圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.37,0:14:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不夠18圓,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,623圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.14,0:14:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道,這個不買了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.12,0:14:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,這麼一點錢\N果然買不了什麼好東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望能買一束玫瑰花給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.90,0:14:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好漂亮喔,謝謝你,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.07,0:14:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到這麼美麗的花\N我覺得好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.77,0:14:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我借錢去買,終於有價值了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.64,0:14:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你居然為了我去借錢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.24,0:14:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.66,0:14:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看,湯要放兩杯水…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.90,0:15:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!水…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.64,0:15:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.28,0:15:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好難過喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.45,0:15:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹做的菜太好吃了\N結果吃太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳還好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.79,0:15:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來探病的,妳拿去吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.23,0:15:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是,一點小東西\N不過代表我的誠意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.26,0:15:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快吃,快點趁熱吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.10,0:15:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷了就不好吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.11,0:15:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.88,0:15:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.78,0:15:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃,真的很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.48,0:15:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,這麼多…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.92,0:15:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣,儘管吃\N請全部吃光光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.09,0:15:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊\N這是專程買來給妳吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.56,0:16:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我當然會吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.98,0:16:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,我終於做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.52,0:16:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吃太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好難過喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.09,0:16:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,我可以進去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代?請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.70,0:16:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.67,0:16:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說妳的肚子可能餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我一點心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.34,0:16:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.68,0:16:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他這種表情,我實在拒絕不了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.98,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的波斯菊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.02,0:17:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是院子裡的\N我摘來代替玫瑰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.09,0:17:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會冷掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.02,0:17:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我最喜歡波斯菊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.16,0:17:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麵會糊掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼我就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.82,0:17:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃,真的很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部吃光光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.64,0:17:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.65,0:18:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼難吃的拉麵她居然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真的好善良喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!鯛魚燒和章魚燒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.41,0:18:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,她全部吃光光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.15,0:18:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還煮了拉麵給她吃嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.92,0:18:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前還吃了三鷹教練的料理呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.42,0:18:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,既然這樣就明說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那種狀況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.03,0:18:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員還把那一大碗\N難吃的拉麵都吃下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還笑嘻嘻地說很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.36,0:18:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是她的偉大之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.37,0:18:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕!糟糕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.27,0:19:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續被當作病人看待的話\N我真的會受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.15,0:19:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.48,0:19:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要開門進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.83,0:19:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.67,0:19:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.74,0:19:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底出了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要看!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.52,0:19:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.92,0:19:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你居然趁管理員行動不便的時候\N闖進來做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.59,0:19:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是看錯你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.59,0:19:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀況\N怎麼看都不像是誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.73,0:19:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員\N妳怎麼不給他兩巴掌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.93,0:20:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的\N我只是想把身體擦一擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛,真無趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說這是一場誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.57,0:20:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.61,0:20:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我突然開門進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.05,0:20:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說了,請把門關上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.68,0:20:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.95,0:20:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.66,0:20:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胃腸藥,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.10,0:20:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼,那個教練又來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.24,0:20:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你,營養午餐剩下的麵包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.64,0:20:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的什麼都吃耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.65,0:20:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃太多?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.62,0:20:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,肚子不太舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.22,0:20:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜,今天我本來想做\N我最拿手的奶油焗蝦給妳吃說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.89,0:20:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.02,0:20:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.53,0:21:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上很抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.03,0:21:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玫瑰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.51,0:21:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你頭上那個傷是怎麼來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.68,0:21:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.78,0:21:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,是被那個臉盆打到的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.92,0:21:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,這點傷算不了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.02,0:21:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,因為我扔得太用力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,是我自己不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.99,0:21:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.99,0:21:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要放在心上啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.93,0:21:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.19,0:21:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.76,0:21:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不浪費材料\N我還是來做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.20,0:21:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你幫忙吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.37,0:21:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹做的料理很好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.74,0:21:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.24,0:21:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是五代\N你額頭那個傷是怎麼來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.25,0:21:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.61,0:21:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我跟管理員之間的祕密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.62,0:21:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.89,0:22:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,過來幫我開個罐頭好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.23,0:22:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.90,0:22:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,出了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.30,0:22:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,開好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.14,0:22:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.94,0:22:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是祕密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.21,0:22:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想叫你把盤子拿給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.58,0:22:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼,早說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.55,0:22:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盤子,盤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.75,0:22:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.42,0:22:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.52,0:22:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.69,0:22:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.56,0:22:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正一定沒什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.40,0:22:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.23,0:22:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.93,0:22:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?什麼?聽不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.74,0:22:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.90,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.04,0:22:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嫁給三鷹的人,一定會很幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.85,0:23:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,我自己也這麼認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.62,0:23:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嫁給我的話,一定會很幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.82,0:23:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.66,0:23:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你也這麼認為吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.73,0:23:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.73,0:23:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣,我只是隨便說說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.87,0:23:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的只是一般的看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.00,0:23:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩位,不要這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.21,0:23:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.10,0:23:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠跟初戀情人結婚\N是很幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.67,0:23:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為能跟那個人結婚的話\N就不用體驗到分手的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.34,0:23:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.01,0:24:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「響子的初戀故事\N總是在下雨天」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.78,0:24:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會為我撐傘的惣一郎\N已經不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.53,0:24:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天在陌生的城市下了一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.54,0:24:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳非常在意淋溼的高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.55,0:24:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前妳用那隱藏著\N稚氣的側臉和我交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.42,0:24:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的話語至今仍能想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.53,0:25:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就彷佛\N置身電影中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.30,0:25:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳輕聲細語地說著\N安靜的最後一幕
